3,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"華人思維: 非友即敵<br />\n西方人思維: 多元包容"},{"pid":"e63e4278a0616e237a7b31985b7044e8f1ac8810","tid":2461993,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"唔知仲以為布係總統，登好似啞撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e86ee411eb4a45869af00ee096a0e034a353252","tid":2461993,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"同後果自負有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31e48ab1d2710054ba0daba45e3dcbc36b61d54","tid":2461993,"uid":9542,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"民主共和黨做法唔同姐<br />\n<br />\n共和自希殊起鐘意玩單邊霸權，好似擅自打伊拉克，整到係國際社會黑鳩憎，侵就開頭掠軍費掠錢但又唔比著數又唔尊重，後尾衰左先黎玩聯合，但都好脅迫式，同埋人地已經唔信美國，中歐協議就係一例<br />\n<br />\n宜家美國姿態降低返，令其實覺得係平起平坐公平對等，覺得可以有返偈傾，當然得唔得以後先知<br />\n<br />\n但宜家話就話比人揀，但美國已經將其他國家利益放埋上枱 eg 同支仔講台日問題、又暗示會監察中歐協議，建立保障各方利益既聯合陣線，孤立支仔，加埋支仔呢排發晒癲，其他發達國家已經開始好難離棄美國同支仔deal"},{"pid":"182328be523ec7e65b7dea8c5f2fc630e493e0c7","tid":2461993,"uid":19012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e63e4278a0616e237a7b31985b7044e8f1ac8810","tid":2461993,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"唔知仲以為布係總統，登好似啞撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"我咁大個仔 第一次見識美國總統係隱佐形<br />\n<br />\n重要自己攪佐篤蘇州屎（非法移民）就派個副總統去處理<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749ebafd7099932a1aad2352a26943b85a6e699b","tid":2461993,"uid":380132,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:13:33.000Z","msg":"開完會比人恰到上心口,仲係到左膠上身<br />\n比trump 一早加1000億關税"},{"pid":"9fcf3a3101154f8eaa8aec1ec3bce622c381c482","tid":2461993,"uid":365765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"有本事就出兵，唔係就同我含撚啦<br />\n講我唔識咩，我坐你得個位啦<br />\n利申：本人絕不同意拜登政府所有對中國不利政策，本人不會違反國安法"},{"pid":"bdcde10a3a6159b7e9484925630414593f5db034","tid":2461993,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:17:02.000Z","msg":"其實美國宜家做法同共產黨啲策略一樣，建立聯合陣線、孤立對方、再逐個擊破，不過只係共產黨完左再逐個清算，加埋呢排發晒癲，義和團式戰狼，連自已咁多年起家方式都離棄埋，比美國攞左去用，形勢掉返轉晒"},{"pid":"ea4f0bbcba90d238f91169e2d33807137a3faa65","tid":2461993,"uid":92188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"我唔係逼你，但你都係民主嘅一員，你自己諗喇"},{"pid":"03a5afafbb52611ea88d9e15b899a66c2effc949","tid":2461993,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40d699e457591790fb31029fe179d055a4b003d","tid":2461993,"uid":142233,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7aed082d3d6986216a8e5a5ac33cfb219c89ed32","tid":2461993,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f3f093400463dfc76b315c8195598dad231c84","tid":2461993,"uid":142233,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"佢唔想逼得太緊姐<br />\n但有啲嘢唔講得出口㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"其實都算講出口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:04:07.000Z","msg":"歐盟根本對抗共意識唔強，依家仲要俾位佢地走真係弱智仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" cla